<font color="#ff8c00">www.addic7ed.com</font>

20:53.415 --> 20:58.010
Nothing brings a smile
to the face of an underprivileged child--

20:58.011 --> 20:59.778
- ( Moans )
- Hi, I'm talking.

20:59.812 --> 21:02.014
Okay.
...like a-- Oh.

21:02.548 --> 21:03.782
Okay, that's wet.
Cut!

21:03.816 --> 21:06.317
Stop. I'm wet.
Something just went wet on me.

21:06.352 --> 21:07.819
Can't we just CGI
these suckers in?

21:07.854 --> 21:09.888
- <i>Dogs, babies, everybody!</i>
<i>- ( Child crying )</i>

21:09.922 --> 21:11.757
Oh, you gotta be--
get your hand out of my mouth!

21:11.791 --> 21:13.925
You gotta be kidding me!
This whole thing better...

21:13.960 --> 21:18.960
- That went viral pretty quick.
- I am not getting that promotion.

